---
// About.astro
---
<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
	<h2 class="section-title reveal">About</h2>
	<div class="title-divider reveal"></div>
	
	<div class="about-grid">
		<!-- Left: Professional human summary statement -->
		<div class="about-bio-container reveal">
			<p class="about-bio">
				I’m a CSE student from Mysuru who likes building complete products, not just UI mockups. Most of my work sits around AI tools, fintech ideas, and interfaces that are simple enough for real people to use. I learn by shipping projects, improving them, and turning rough ideas into usable products.
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Right/Bottom: 3 Clean Premium cards -->
		<div class="about-cards-grid reveal">
			<div class="card-premium about-card">
				<div class="card-icon icon-yellow">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline></svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="card-title">Builder mindset</h3>
				<p class="card-text">I learn by shipping.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="card-premium about-card">
				<div class="card-icon icon-blue">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"></line><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"></path></svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="card-title">Current focus</h3>
				<p class="card-text">AI tools, fintech, and clean interfaces.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="card-premium about-card">
				<div class="card-icon icon-green">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="card-title">Favorite stack</h3>
				<p class="card-text">Python, Next.js, Supabase.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	#about {
		position: relative;
	}

	.title-divider {
		width: 40px;
		height: 3px;
		background: var(--accent-blue);
		border-radius: 2px;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.about-grid {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	.about-bio-container {
		max-width: 800px;
	}

	.about-bio {
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		font-weight: 450;
	}

	.about-cards-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.about-card {
		padding: 2.2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1.2rem;
	}

	.card-icon {
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.icon-yellow {
		background: rgba(251, 188, 4, 0.08);
		color: var(--accent-yellow);
	}

	.icon-blue {
		background: rgba(26, 115, 232, 0.08);
		color: var(--accent-blue);
	}

	.icon-green {
		background: rgba(24, 128, 56, 0.08);
		color: var(--accent-green);
	}

	.card-title {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.card-text {
		font-family: var(--font-sans);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about-cards-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.about-card {
			padding: 1.8rem;
		}
	}
</style>
